      It will be able to recognize all types of hp48's objects (with the use of libraries).
      So you 'll can display or modify any programs (such as changing pictures of your
      favorite game).
      All registered users will have informations concerning the disponibility of it.
@ENDNODE

@NODE "Bug" "Bugs"
@TOC "MAIN"


        -If the program doesn't display a picture (if the color of the screen is a
	 dark black). Don't panic the picture is really here.
        -Some problems with Screen opening and ZOOM (Problem with screen's sizes).
	-Never load a file larger than 32ko (or 64ko in ASCII) otherwise it will
         be truncated.

@ENDNODE

